Parameters:
soapLogin - Your Vindicia soap login for the Vindicia server you are sending your requests to
soapPassword - Your Vindicia soap password for the Vindicia server you are sending your requests to
soapTokenObject - Token object as generated by AXIS soap stubs
Method Detail

fetch

public VindiciaReturn fetch(java.lang.String srd)
                     throws VindiciaServiceException
Loads a previously created dtlink=Token object.The object to load is specified by setting VID or merchantTokenId in the input object

Has the following return values:

'400:Identifier not specified' if neither VID nor merchantTokenId was specified
'404:Unable to load token' The specified VID or merchantTokenId was not found

Parameters:
srd - sparse return descriptor
Returns:
object containing information about success, failure, etc for this call
Throws:
VindiciaServiceException
